{"tid":292811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警列「牙籤弩」為武器　藏有或管有隨時犯法","createTime":"2017-06-21T16:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-22T10:57:44.000Z","uid":20933,"like":16,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e23af58b0fdc88595ecdddb4cb44026897fab50b","tid":292811,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:03:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170621/large/1498056525_20f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170621%2Flarge%2F1498056525_20f5.jpg&h=e287d362&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引起中港澳家長關注的中國玩具「牙籤弩」，雖然暫未有發現流入香港，但因其殺傷力極大，已令全城家長恐慌。就此事件，警方今日亦再作回應稱十分關注事，並列明在公眾地方管有「牙籤弩」會觸犯《公安條例》的「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」，一經定罪，最高刑罰監禁3年。<br />\n<br />\n就近日一種名為「牙籤弩」的小型武器在網上售賣，這武器可將牙籤射出，具有殺傷力，可能造成嚴重身體傷害。警方十分關注此事宜，雖然至今未有接獲相關舉報，但市民若發現任何與此武器有關的事件，請通知警方，警方必定積極跟進。<br />\n<br />\n就現時資料顯示，在公眾地方管有「牙籤弩」會觸犯《公安條例》第33條的「在公眾地方管有攻擊性武器」，一經定罪，最高刑罰監禁3年。而管有此種武器，意圖作非法用途則會觸犯《簡易程序治罪條例》第17條「管有攻擊性武器，並有所意圖」，最高可處罰款$5,000或監禁2年。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民，特別是年輕人及其家長，不可輕視「牙籤弩」的殺傷力，而且藏有或使用這武器會違反香港法例，如造成實際人身傷害，則會觸犯更嚴重的刑事罪行，切勿以身試法。"},{"pid":"3c2cffc89fd25a5ada1237135ea472adc8504f9c","tid":292811,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:03:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170621&amp;guid=56859862&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170621%26guid%3D56859862%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=PyUhZ76huSLlXyCr9gH8PsmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=46a36f8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170621%26guid%3D56859862%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=98bdd0b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170621&amp;guid=56859862&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"9cef38d4499bfd14d7744a7bee696c823324862f","tid":292811,"uid":97814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"09856895516dcf5525af1f50e962b50e8fa71671","tid":292811,"uid":3717,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:07:17.000Z","msg":"想當年我射碼子都有咁既威力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8828b639ee8c447506f745daa399a1874fdf54ea","tid":292811,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:13:42.000Z","msg":"咁弓箭都係啦"},{"pid":"598dca9323b1ac4f4bbd46fe4a6f438bb88d5798","tid":292811,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:15:56.000Z","msg":"BB彈槍呢？"},{"pid":"56c37167a7b50abf20a323a42dfa42b7438ea4fa","tid":292811,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8461fdf8b8ed8f88136d08725b496e24923fe7","tid":292811,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"用攻擊性武器屈人基本上任何美勞用工具都鎖得"},{"pid":"96e6e1a3e1cb6cbc1089771ba9978654cf9c03f7","tid":292811,"uid":55614,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:28:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用攻擊性武器屈人基本上任何美勞用工具都鎖得</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  帶鉸剪出街 犯法 !<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  呀sir, 頭先買架喎<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有意圖作為攻擊性武器 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a4fd704d1dbb0707f4f75dc5e2e5f5e23d46b22","tid":292811,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T16:29:04.000Z","msg":"呀係，雨遮都係攻擊性武器"},{"pid":"91b1a44ead6e57bcaa43e0994fccf9e6d0d5c10c","tid":292811,"uid":44454,"like":1